The article is a letter from Joseph R. Biden Jr., addressed to the Chairman or Chairwoman, regarding changes to the legal and policy frameworks for the United States' use of military force and national security operations. The letter is in accordance with section 1264(b) of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2018. The letter includes an unclassified notice and a classified annex, which contains the Presidential Policy Memorandum outlining the changes. The letter is signed by Joseph R. Biden Jr.